data.description: Welcome to a beautiful 2022 top of the line Norris home on a quiet and peaceful 0.46+/- lot right near the river. This home features a spacious open concept kitchen, dining and living area with a large island in the kitchen, an entertainment area in the living room and a back deck off of the dining area. With drywall all throughout, this home truly is gorgeous! The mud room / laundry room has a large utility sink with ample storage and counter space. Taxes are estimated by the county, as the home has not been placed long enough to know exactly what they will be. Take a look at the 3D virtual tour included here, and schedule your viewing of this gorgeous home today!
